title: WEDNESDAY 5/19 - JULIO JONES' FUTURE IN ATLANTA
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 5/19 - JULIO JONES' FUTURE IN ATLANTA
description:
Matt Ryan (0:10) discusses Julio Jones' future with the Falcons. Darius Leonard (1:12) hopes to remain with the Colts long-term. Kyle Shanahan (2:02) talks about the importance of Nick Bosa's return to the 49ers defense. Cam Heyward (2:53) happy to see Najee Harris with the Steelers...and Patrick Surtain II (3:37) signs with the Broncos
